thread.title: Rita Freling
thread.title_full: Premium Mortgage reviewed by Rita Freling

author: Rita Freling
title: Rita Freling
text:
I have sold Real Estate for 30 years and never, have I received the service and follow up that I have had with Jerry Frate and Kim Evert, his processor.
They are prompt in calling you back if you leave a message and never fail to follow up with my buyers.
They have given me and my clients the best service and attention possible. I would and do, refer them to everyone.
Thank you Premium! You're the BEST !
Rita Freling
REMAX Plus
